      "endLine": 37,
      "source": "memory",
      "snippet": "**The Ian reframe** is the sharpest strategic move to come out of this. Right now you're doing ~3 hours of project work for $500 under the retainer structure. The pivot: go to Ian and say \"this project work is the business we're spinning off -- pay you a referral fee for every client from your audience.\" Ian's supportive. July 9 webinar (~1,000 sellers) is the launch vehicle for this as a standalone product. **Niche locked: coaching.** No more vending groups, no more custom one-offs. Coaching AI product. Website + Stripe. That's the unlock. Daniel said it, Gorski's framework confirmed it. **What's blocking scale right now:** website, bank account, entity structure, productized offer. Four",
